      "content": "okay i get the \"battle plan\" thing for the layout. but i was wondering more about what happens inside the concrete itself once it's all set. like, since the rebar is hidden deep inside the solid slab, are there any specific things engineers worry about regarding the bond between the steel and the concrete? i mean, if they don't stick together well, does the whole system fail?",
